quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  33,60,"Sε nkͻnkͻnsafoͻ no, ne wͻn a yadeε wͻ wͻn akoma mu no, ne wͻn a wͻ’di nsekuro no a wͻn wͻ Madina no anyae (wͻn suban bͻne no) a, Yε’de wͻn bεhyε wonsa, na wͻ’nntumi ne wo mmͻ afipam wͻ (kuro no) mu gyesε (berε) tiaa bi"
  33,61,Ya’dome wͻn; baabiara a yεnsa bεka wͻn no yεbεkye wͻn aku wͻn kum paa
  33,62,Nyankopͻn kwan a εda hͻ wͻ wͻn a wͻ’adikan atwa mu kͻ no ho ne no; na wonhunu nsakraeε wͻ kwan a Nyankopͻn atwa ato hͻ no mu
  33,63,"Nnipa no rebisa wo Dͻnhwere no ho asεm. Ka sε: “Ɛho nimdeε no deε Nyankopͻn nko ara hͻ na εwͻ”. Na deεn na εbεkyerε wo sε ebia Dͻnhwere no abεn"
  33,64,"Nokorε sε Nyankopͻn adome boniayεfoͻ no, na Wasiesie Ogya tanaa ato hͻ ama wͻn"
  33,65,"Emu na wͻ’bεtena afe bͻͻ, na wͻ’nnya okyitaafoͻ anaa ͻboafoͻ (biara)"
  33,66,"Ԑda a yεbԑdane wͻn anim abutu egya no mu no, wͻ’bεka sε: “Sε yehunui a anka yεyεε sotie maa Nyankopͻn san yεε sotie maa Ͻsomafoͻ no”"
  33,67,"Wͻ’bεka sε: “Ye’Wura Nyankopͻn, yedii yεn nhemfo ne yεn mpanimfoͻ nom akyi εna wͻ’yeraa yεn frii kwan (tenenee) no soͻ”"
  33,68,"Ye’Wura Nyankopͻn, (yεsrε Wo sε): “Ma wͻn asotwee no mmͻho mmienu, na fa nnomee a εsoo paa dome wͻn.”"
  33,69,"Mo a moagye adie, monhwε na moanyε sε wͻn a wͻ’hyεε Mose abufuo na Nyankopͻn sanee neho fri deε wͻ’ka (detoo no soͻ) no ho no; na ͻyε (onipa a) ͻwͻ animuonyam wͻ Nyankopͻn hͻ"
  33,70,"Mo a moagye adie, monsuro Nyankopͻn na (εberε biara mu no) monka kasa pa"
  33,71,"Ɔbεma monyuma ayε yie ama mo, na Ɔde mobͻne akyε mo; na obi a ͻbεyε sotie ama Nyankopͻn ne Nesomafoͻ no, εyε nokorε a esipi sε wadi nkonim a εsoo paa"
  33,72,"Nokorε sε, Yε’de nhwεsodeε maa ͻsoro ne asaase ne mmepͻ, nanso wͻn ampene sε wͻ’bεgye ato wͻn ho soͻ, na wͻ’nyaa ho suro, εna onipa gye soaeε. Nokorε sε, ͻyε omimfo, ogyegyentwie"
  33,73,"Sεdeε Nyankopͻn bεtwe nkͻnkͻnsafoͻ mmarima ne nkͻnkͻnsafoͻ mmaa ne abosomsomfoͻ mmarima ne abosomsomfoͻ mmaa no aso, na Ͻbεgye agyidiefoͻ mmarima ne agyidiefoͻ mmaa no adwen sakra. Nyankopͻn ne Bͻnefakyε Hene, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene"
  34,1,"Aseda wͻ Nyankopͻn no a deε εwͻ soro ne deε εwͻ asaase so nyinaa yε Ne dea no; aseda no san wͻ no wͻ Daakye no nso. Ɔne Onyansafoͻ no, Ɔne biribiara ho Amanebͻ Wura no"
  34,2,"Onim deε εkͻ asaase mu, ne deε epue firi mu, ne deε esiane firi soro ne deε εforo kͻ hͻ, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no, Bͻnefakyε Wura no"
  34,3,"Boniayεfoͻ no ka sε: “Dͻnhwere no mma yεn so biara”. Kasε: ‘’Aane, Mede me Wura, Ahuntasεm mu Nimdefoͻ no di nse sε, εbεba mo so. Deε emu duro ketekete tesε aboboaa a (onipa) ani ntumi nhunu wͻ soro anaasε asaase so anaasε deε esua kyεn saa anaasε deε εso kyεn saa mmpa ne ho, na mmom (nenyinaa) wͻ Nwoma pefee no mu"
  34,4,Sεdeε Obetua wͻn a wͻ’agye adie na wͻ’di dwuma pa no ka. Saa nkorͻfoͻ no wͻ bͻnefakyε ne akyεdeε a animuonyam wͻ mu
  34,5,Wͻn a wͻ’bͻ mmͻden kotia Yεn Nsεm no sԑdeԑ ԑbԑyԑ kwa no benya asotwee akatua a εyε ya paa
  34,6,"Wͻn a yama wͻn nimdeε no hunu sε deε yasiane afiri wo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ abrε woͻ no ne Nokorε no, na εkyerε kwan kͻ Otumfoͻ Ayeyie Wura no kwan no so"
  34,7,"Wͻn a wͻ’yi boniayε no ka sε: “Yεnkyerε mo onipa bi a ͻreka kyerε mo sε, sε (mowu na) mo mu tete pasapasa a, nokorε sε mobεsan ayε abͻdeε foforͻ"
  34,8,Nkontompo na ͻretwa to Nyankopͻn soͻ anaasε wabͻ dam?” Daabi; wͻn a wͻ’nnye Daakye no nnie no wͻ asotwee ne ͻyera a εkͻ akyirikyiri paa mu
  34,9,"Enti wͻ’nhunuu deε εda wͻn anim ne deε εda wͻn akyi a εyε ͻsoro ne asaase? Sε Yε’pε a Yε’bεma wͻn amem wͻ asaase no mu, anaasε Yε’bεma ͻsoro no fa bi (ate) abεhwe wͻn so. Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu de ma akoa biara a ͻdane ne ho ma (Nyankopͻn)"